tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",119,174,"耶和華阿、我切慕你的救恩．你的律法也是我所喜愛的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",119,175,"願我的性命存活、得以讚美你．願你的典章幫助我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",119,176,"我如亡羊走迷了路．求你尋找僕人．因我不忘記你的命令。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,1,"〔上行〔或作登階下同〕之詩。〕我在急難中求告耶和華、他就應允我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,2,"耶和華阿、求你救我脫離說謊的嘴唇、和詭詐的舌頭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,3,"詭詐的舌頭阿、要給你甚麼呢。要拿甚麼加給你呢．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,4,"就是勇士的利箭、和羅騰木的炭火。〔羅騰小樹名松類〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,5,"我寄居在米設、住在基達帳棚之中、有禍了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,6,"我與那恨惡和睦的人、許久同住。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",120,7,"我願和睦．但我發言、他們就要爭戰。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,1,"〔上行之詩。〕我要向山舉目。我的幫助從何而來。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,2,"我的幫助從造天地的耶和華而來。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,3,"他必不叫你的腳搖動．保護你的必不打盹。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,4,"保護以色列的、也不打盹、也不睡覺。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,5,"保護你的是耶和華．耶和華在你右邊蔭庇你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,6,"白日太陽必不傷你．夜間月亮必不害你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,7,"耶和華要保護你、免受一切的災害．他要保護你的性命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",121,8,"你出你入、耶和華要保護你、從今時直到永遠。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,1,"〔大衛上行之詩。〕人對我說、我們往耶和華的殿去、我就歡喜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,2,"耶路撒冷阿、我們的腳、站在你的門內。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,3,"耶路撒冷被建造、如同連絡整齊的一座城。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,4,"眾支派、就是耶和華的支派、上那裡去、按以色列的常例、〔或作作以色列的證據〕稱讚耶和華的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,5,"因為在那裡設立審判的寶座、就是大衛家的寶座。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,6,"你們要為耶路撒冷求平安。耶路撒冷阿、愛你的人必然興旺。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,7,"願你城中平安、願你宮內興旺。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,8,"因我弟兄和同伴的緣故、我要說、願平安在你中間。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",122,9,"因耶和華我們　神殿的緣故、我要為你求福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",123,1,"〔上行之詩。〕坐在天上的主阿、我向你舉目。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",123,2,"看哪、僕人的眼睛怎樣望主人的手、使女的眼睛怎樣望主母的手、我們的眼睛也照樣望耶和華我們的　神、直到他憐憫我們。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",123,3,"耶和華阿、求你憐憫我們、憐憫我們．因為我們被藐視、已到極處。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",123,4,"我們被那些安逸人的譏誚、和驕傲人的藐視、已到極處。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,1,"〔大衛上行之詩。〕以色列人要說、若不是耶和華幫助我們、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,2,"若不是耶和華幫助我們、當人起來攻擊我們、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,3,"向我們發怒的時候、就把我們活活的吞了．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,4,"那時、波濤必漫過我們、河水必淹沒我們．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,5,"狂傲的水必淹沒我們。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,6,"耶和華是應當稱頌的．他沒有把我們當野食交給他們吞喫。〔原文作牙齒〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,7,"我們好像雀鳥從捕鳥人的網羅裡逃脫．網羅破裂、我們逃脫了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",124,8,"我們得幫助、是在乎倚靠造天地之耶和華的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",125,1,"〔上行之詩。〕倚靠耶和華的人、好像錫安山、永不動搖。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",125,2,"眾山怎樣圍繞耶路撒冷、耶和華也照樣圍繞他的百姓、從今時直到永遠。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",125,3,"惡人的杖、不常落在義人的分上、免得義人伸手作惡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",125,4,"耶和華阿、求你善待那些為善、和心裡正直的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",125,5,"至於那偏行彎曲道路的人、耶和華必使他和作惡的人、一同出去受刑。願平安歸於以色列。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,1,"〔上行之詩。〕當耶和華將那些被擄的帶回錫安的時候、我們好像作夢的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,2,"我們滿口喜笑、滿舌歡呼的時候、外邦中就有人說、耶和華為他們行了大事。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,3,"耶和華果然為我們行了大事、我們就歡喜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,4,"耶和華阿、求你使我們被擄的人歸回、好像南地的河水復流。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,5,"流淚撒種的、必歡呼收割。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",126,6,"那帶種流淚出去的、必要歡歡樂樂的帶禾捆回來。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",127,1,"〔所羅門上行之詩。〕若不是耶和華建造房屋、建造的人就枉然勞力．若不是耶和華看守城池、看守的人就枉然儆醒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",127,2,"你們清晨早起、夜晚安歇、喫勞碌得來的飯、本是枉然．惟有耶和華所親愛的、必叫他安然睡覺。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",127,3,"兒女是耶和華所賜的產業．所懷的胎、是他所給的賞賜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",127,4,"少年時所生的兒女、好像勇士手中的箭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",127,5,"箭袋充滿的人、便為有福．他們在城門口、和仇敵說話的時候、必不至於羞愧。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,1,"〔上行之詩。〕凡敬畏耶和華、遵行他道的人、便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,2,"你要喫勞碌得來的．你要享福、事情順利。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,3,"你妻子在你的內室、好像多結果子的葡萄樹．你兒女圍繞你的桌子、好像橄欖栽子。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,4,"看哪、敬畏耶和華的人、必要這樣蒙福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,5,"願耶和華從錫安賜福給你。願你一生一世、看見耶路撒冷的好處。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",128,6,"願你看見你兒女的兒女。願平安歸於以色列。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,1,"〔上行之詩。〕以色列當說、從我幼年以來、敵人屢次苦害我、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,2,"從我幼年以來、敵人屢次苦害我、卻沒有勝了我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,3,"如同扶犁的、在我背上扶犁而耕．耕的犁溝甚長。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,4,"耶和華是公義的．他砍斷了惡人的繩索。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,5,"願恨惡錫安的、都蒙羞退後。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,6,"願他們像房頂上的草、未長成而枯乾．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,7,"收割的不夠一把、捆禾的也不滿懷．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",129,8,"過路的也不說、願耶和華所賜的福、歸與你們．我們奉耶和華的名、給你們祝福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,1,"〔上行之詩。〕耶和華阿、我從深處向你求告。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,2,"主阿、求你聽我的聲音．願你側耳聽我懇求的聲音。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,3,"主耶和華阿、你若究察罪孽、誰能站得住呢．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,4,"但在你有赦免之恩、要叫人敬畏你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,5,"我等候耶和華、我的心等候．我也仰望他的話。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,6,"我的心等候主、勝於守夜的等候天亮、勝於守夜的等候天亮。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,7,"以色列阿、你當仰望耶和華．因他有慈愛、有豐盛的救恩。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",130,8,"他必救贖以色列脫離一切的罪孽。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",131,1,"〔大衛上行之詩。〕耶和華阿、我的心不狂傲、我的眼不高大．重大和測不透的事、我也不敢行。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",131,2,"我的心平穩安靜、好像斷過奶的孩子在他母親的懷中．我的心在我裡面真像斷過奶的孩子。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",131,3,"以色列阿、你當仰望耶和華、從今時直到永遠。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,1,"〔上行之詩。〕耶和華阿、求你記念大衛所受的一切苦難．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,2,"他怎樣向耶和華起誓、向雅各的大能者許願、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,3,"說、我必不進我的帳幕、也不上我的床榻．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,4,"我不容我的眼睛睡覺、也不容我的眼目打盹．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,5,"直等我為耶和華尋得所在、為雅各的大能者尋得居所。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,6,"我們聽說約櫃在以法他．我們在基列耶琳就尋見了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,7,"我們要進他的居所、在他腳凳前下拜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,8,"耶和華阿、求你興起、和你有能力的約櫃同入安息之所。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,9,"願你的祭司披上公義．願你的聖民歡呼。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,10,"求你因你僕人大衛的緣故、不要厭棄你的受膏者。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,11,"耶和華向大衛憑誠實起了誓、必不反覆、說、我要使你所生的坐在你的寶座上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,12,"你的眾子若守我的約、和我所教訓他們的法度、他們的子孫、必永遠坐在你的寶座上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,13,"因為耶和華揀選了錫安、願意當作自己的居所、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,14,"說、這是我永遠安息之所．我要住在這裡．因為是我所願意的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,15,"我要使其中的糧食豐滿、使其中的窮人飽足。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,16,"我要使祭司披上救恩、聖民大聲歡呼。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,17,"我要叫大衛的角、在那裡發生．我為我的受膏者、預備明燈。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",132,18,"我要使他的仇敵、披上羞恥．但他的冠冕、要在頭上發光。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",133,1,"〔大衛上行之詩。〕看哪、弟兄和睦同居、是何等的善、何等的美。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",133,2,"這好比那貴重的油、澆在亞倫的頭上、流到鬍鬚．又流到他的衣襟．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",133,3,"又好比黑門的甘露、降在錫安山．因為在那裡有耶和華所命定的福、就是永遠的生命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",134,1,"〔上行之詩。〕耶和華的僕人、夜間站在耶和華殿中的、你們當稱頌耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",134,2,"你們當向聖所舉手、稱頌耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",134,3,"願造天地的耶和華、從錫安賜福給你們。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,1,"你們要讚美耶和華。你們要讚美耶和華的名。耶和華的僕人、站在耶和華殿中、站在我們　神殿院中的、你們要讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,2,"見上節")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,3,"你們要讚美耶和華．耶和華本為善．要歌頌他的名、因為這是美好的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,4,"耶和華揀選雅各歸自己、揀選以色列特作自己的子民。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,5,"原來我知道耶和華為大、也知道我們的主超乎萬神之上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,6,"耶和華在天上、在地下、在海中、在一切的深處、都隨自己的意旨而行．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,7,"他使雲霧從地極上騰、造電隨雨而閃、從府庫中帶出風來．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,8,"他將埃及頭生的、連人帶牲畜、都擊殺了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,9,"埃及阿、他施行神蹟奇事在你當中、在法老和他一切臣僕身上．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,10,"他擊殺許多的民、又殺戮大能的王、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,11,"就是亞摩利王西宏、和巴珊王噩、並迦南一切的國王、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,12,"將他們的地、賞賜他的百姓以色列為業。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,13,"耶和華阿、你的名存到永遠．耶和華阿、你可記念的名、存到萬代。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,14,"耶和華要為他的百姓伸冤、為他的僕人後悔。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,15,"外邦的偶像、是金的銀的、是人手所造的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,16,"有口卻不能言．有眼卻不能看．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,17,"有耳卻不能聽．口中也沒有氣息。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,18,"造他的要和他一樣．凡靠他的、也要如此。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,19,"以色列家阿、你們要稱頌耶和華．亞倫家阿、你們要稱頌耶和華．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,20,"利未家阿、你們要稱頌耶和華．你們敬畏耶和華的、要稱頌耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",135,21,"住在耶路撒冷的耶和華、該從錫安受稱頌。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,1,"你們要稱謝耶和華、因他本為善．他的慈愛永遠長存。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,2,"你們要稱謝萬神之神、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,3,"你們要稱謝萬主之主、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,4,"稱謝那獨行大奇事的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,5,"稱謝那用智慧造天的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,6,"稱謝那鋪地在水以上的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,7,"稱謝那造成大光的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,8,"他造日頭管白晝、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,9,"他造月亮星宿管黑夜、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,10,"稱謝那擊殺埃及人之長子的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,11,"他領以色列人從他們中間出來、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,12,"他施展大能的手、和伸出來的膀臂、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,13,"稱謝那分裂紅海的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,14,"他領以色列從其中經過、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,15,"卻把法老和他的軍兵推翻在紅海裡、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,16,"稱謝那引導自己的民行走曠野的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,17,"稱謝那擊殺大君王的、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,18,"他殺戮有名的君王、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,19,"就是殺戮亞摩利王西宏、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,20,"又殺巴珊王噩、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,21,"他將他們的地賜他的百姓為業、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,22,"就是賜他的僕人以色列為業、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,23,"他顧念我們在卑微的地步、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,24,"他救拔我們脫離敵人、因他的慈愛永遠長存．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,25,"他賜糧食給凡有血氣的、因他的慈愛永遠長存。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",136,26,"你們要稱謝天上的　神、因他的慈愛永遠長存。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,1,"我們曾在巴比倫的河邊坐下、一追想錫安就哭了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,2,"我們把琴掛在那裡的柳樹上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,3,"因為在那裡擄掠我們的、要我們唱歌、搶奪我們的、要我們作樂、說、給我們唱一首錫安歌罷。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,4,"我們怎能在外邦唱耶和華的歌呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,5,"耶路撒冷阿、我若忘記你、情願我的右手忘記技巧。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,6,"我若不記念你、若不看耶路撒冷過於我所最喜樂的、情願我的舌頭貼於上膛。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,7,"耶路撒冷遭難的日子、以東人說拆毀、拆毀、直拆到根基．耶和華阿、求你記念這仇。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,8,"將要被滅的巴比倫城阿、〔城原文作女子〕報復你、像你待我們的、那人便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",137,9,"拿你的嬰孩摔在磐石上的、那人便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,1,"〔大衛的詩。〕我要一心稱謝你、在諸神面前歌頌你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,2,"我要向你的聖殿下拜、為你的慈愛和誠實稱讚你的名．因你使你的話顯為大、過於你所應許的。〔或作超乎你的名聲〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,3,"我呼求的日子、你就應允我、鼓勵我、使我心裡有能力。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,4,"耶和華阿、地上的君王、都要稱謝你、因他們聽見了你口中的言語。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,5,"他們要歌頌耶和華的作為．因耶和華大有榮耀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,6,"耶和華雖高、仍看顧低微的人．他卻從遠處看出驕傲的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,7,"我雖行在患難中、你必將我救活．我的仇敵發怒、你必伸手抵擋他們、你的右手也必救我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",138,8,"耶和華必成全關乎我的事．耶和華阿、你的慈愛永遠長存．求你不要離棄你手所造的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,1,"〔大衛的詩、交與伶長。〕耶和華阿、你已經鑒察我、認識我．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,2,"我坐下、我起來、你都曉得．你從遠處知道我的意念。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,3,"我行路、我躺臥、你都細察、你也深知我一切所行的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,4,"耶和華阿、我舌頭上的話、你沒有一句不知道的．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,5,"你在我前後環繞我、按手在我身上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,6,"這樣的知識奇妙、是我不能測的．至高、是我不能及的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,7,"我往那裡去躲避你的靈．我往那裡逃躲避你的面。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,8,"我若升到天上、你在那裡．我若在陰間下榻、你也在那裡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,9,"我若展開清晨的翅膀、飛到海極居住．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,10,"就是在那裡、你的手必引導我．你的右手、也必扶持我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,11,"我若說、黑暗必定遮蔽我、我周圍的亮光必成為黑夜．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,12,"黑暗也不能遮蔽我使你不見、黑夜卻如白晝發亮．黑暗和光明、在你看都是一樣。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,13,"我的肺腑是你所造的．我在母腹中、你已覆庇我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,14,"我要稱謝你、因我受造奇妙可畏．你的作為奇妙．這是我心深知道的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,15,"我在暗中受造、在地的深處被聯絡、那時、我的形體並不向你隱藏。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,16,"我未成形的體質、你的眼早已看見了．你所定的日子、我尚未度一日、〔或作我被造的肢體尚未有其一〕你都寫在你的冊上了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,17,"　神阿、你的意念向我何等寶貴．其數何等眾多。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,18,"我若數點、比海沙更多．我睡醒的時候、仍和你同在。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,19,"　神阿、你必要殺戮惡人．所以你們好流人血的、離開我去罷。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,20,"因為他們說惡言頂撞你、你的仇敵也妄稱你的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,21,"耶和華阿、恨惡你的、我豈不恨惡他們麼．攻擊你的、我豈不憎嫌他們麼。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,22,"我切切的恨惡他們、以他們為仇敵。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,23,"　神阿、求你鑒察我、知道我的心思、試煉我、知道我的意念．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",139,24,"看在我裡面有甚麼惡行沒有、引導我走永生的道路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,1,"〔大衛的詩、交與伶長。〕耶和華阿、求你拯救我脫離兇惡的人、保護我脫離強暴的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,2,"他們心中圖謀奸惡、常常聚集要爭戰。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,3,"他們使舌頭尖利如蛇．嘴裡有虺蛇的毒氣。〔細拉〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,4,"耶和華阿、求你拯救我、脫離惡人的手、保護我、脫離強暴的人．他們圖謀推我跌倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,5,"驕傲人為我暗設網羅和繩索．他們在路旁鋪下網、設下圈套。〔細拉〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,6,"我曾對耶和華說、你是我的　神．耶和華阿、求你留心聽我懇求的聲音。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,7,"主耶和華、我救恩的力量阿、在爭戰的日子、你遮蔽了我的頭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,8,"耶和華阿、求你不要遂惡人的心願．不要成就他們的計謀、恐怕他們自高。〔細拉〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,9,"至於那些昂首圍困我的人、願他們嘴唇的奸惡、陷害〔原文作遮蔽〕自己。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,10,"願火炭落在他們身上．願他們被丟在火中、拋在深坑裡、不能再起來。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,11,"說惡言的人、在地上必堅立不住．禍患必獵取強暴的人、將他打倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,12,"我知道耶和華必為困苦人伸冤、必為窮乏人辨屈。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",140,13,"義人必要稱讚你的名．正直人必住在你面前。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,1,"〔大衛的詩。〕耶和華阿、我曾求告你．求你快快臨到我這裡．我求告你的時候、願你留心聽我的聲音。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,2,"願我的禱告、如香陳列在你面前．願我舉手祈求、如獻晚祭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,3,"耶和華阿、求你禁止我的口、把守我的嘴。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,4,"求你不叫我的心、偏向邪惡、以致我和作孽的人同行惡事．也不叫我喫他們的美食。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,5,"任憑義人擊打我、這算為仁慈．任憑他責備我、這算為頭上的膏油．我的頭不要躲閃。正在他們行惡的時候、我仍要祈禱。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,6,"他們的審判官、被扔在巖下．眾人要聽我的話、因為這話甘甜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,7,"我們的骨頭、散在墓旁、好像人耕田、刨地的土塊。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,8,"主耶和華阿、我的眼目仰望你．我投靠你、求你不要將我撇得孤苦。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,9,"求你保護我脫離惡人為我設的網羅、和作孽之人的圈套。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",141,10,"願惡人落在自己的網裡．我卻得以逃脫。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,1,"〔大衛在洞裡作的訓誨詩、乃是祈禱。〕我發聲哀告耶和華．發聲懇求耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,2,"我在他面前吐露我的苦情．陳說我的患難。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,3,"我的靈在我裡面發昏的時候、你知道我的道路。在我行的路上、敵人為我暗設網羅。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,4,"求你向我右邊觀看、因為沒有人認識我．我無處避難、也沒有人眷顧我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,5,"耶和華阿、我曾向你哀求．我說、你是我的避難所．在活人之地、你是我的福分。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,6,"求你側耳聽我的呼求、因我落到極卑之地．求你救我脫離逼迫我的人、因為他們比我強盛。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",142,7,"求你領我出離被囚之地、我好稱讚你的名．義人必環繞我、因為你是用厚恩待我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,1,"〔大衛的詩。〕耶和華阿、求你聽我的禱告、留心聽我的懇求、憑你的信實和公義應允我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,2,"求你不要審問僕人．因為在你面前凡活著的人、沒有一個是義的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,3,"原來仇敵逼迫我、將我打倒在地．使我住在幽暗之處、像死了許久的人一樣。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,4,"所以我的靈在我裡面發昏．我的心在我裡面悽慘。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,5,"我追想古時之日、思想你的一切作為、默念你手的工作。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,6,"我向你舉手我的心渴想你、如乾旱之地盼雨一樣。〔細拉〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,7,"耶和華阿、求你速速應允我．我心神耗盡．不要向我掩面、免得我像那些下坑的人一樣。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,8,"求你使我清晨得聽你慈愛之言、因我倚靠你．求你使我知道當行的路、因我的心仰望你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,9,"耶和華阿、求你救我脫離我的仇敵．我往你那裡藏身。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,10,"求你指教我遵行你的旨意、因你是我的　神．你的靈本為善．求你引我到平坦之地。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,11,"耶和華阿、求你為你的名將我救活．憑你的公義、將我從患難中領出來．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",143,12,"憑你的慈愛剪除我的仇敵、滅絕一切苦待我的人．因我是你的僕人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,1,"〔大衛的詩。〕耶和華我的磐石、是應當稱頌的．他教導我的手爭戰、教導我的指頭打仗。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,2,"他是我慈愛的主、我的山寨、我的高臺、我的救主、我的盾牌、是我所投靠的．他使我的百姓服在我以下。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,3,"耶和華阿、人算甚麼、你竟認識他．世人算甚麼、你竟顧念他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,4,"人好像一口氣．他的年日如同影兒快快過去。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,5,"耶和華阿、求你使天下垂、親自降臨．摸山、山就冒煙。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,6,"求你發出閃電、使他們四散．射出你的箭、使他們擾亂。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,7,"求你從上伸手救拔我、救我出離大水、救我脫離外邦人的手。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,8,"他們的口說謊話、他們的右手起假誓。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,9,"　神阿、我要向你唱新歌．用十絃瑟向你歌頌。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,10,"你是那拯救君王的．你是那救僕人大衛脫離害命之刀的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,11,"求你救拔我、救我脫離外邦人的手．他們的口說謊話、他們的右手起假誓。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,12,"我們的兒子、從幼年好像樹栽子長大、我們的女兒、如同殿角石、是按建宮的樣式鑿成的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,13,"我們的倉盈滿、能出各樣的糧食、我們的羊、在田間孳生千萬．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,14,"我們的牛馱著滿馱、沒有人闖進來搶奪、也沒有人出去爭戰、我們的街市上、也沒有哭號的聲音．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",144,15,"遇見這光景的百姓、便為有福．有耶和華為他們的　神、這百姓便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,1,"〔大衛的讚美詩。〕我的　神我的王阿、我要尊崇你．我要永永遠遠稱頌你的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,2,"我要天天稱頌你．也要永永遠遠讚美你的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,3,"耶和華本為大、該受大讚美．其大無法測度。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,4,"這代要對那代頌讚你的作為、也要傳揚你的大能。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,5,"我要默念你威嚴的尊榮、和你奇妙的作為。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,6,"人要傳說你可畏之事的能力．我也要傳揚你的大德。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,7,"他們記念你的大恩、就要傳出來、並要歌唱你的公義。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,8,"耶和華有恩惠、有憐憫、不輕易發怒、大有慈愛。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,9,"耶和華善待萬民、他的慈悲、覆庇他一切所造的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,10,"耶和華阿、你一切所造的、都要稱謝你．你的聖民、也要稱頌你、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,11,"傳說你國的榮耀、談論你的大能．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,12,"好叫世人知道你大能的作為、並你國度威嚴的榮耀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,13,"你的國是永遠的國、你執掌的權柄、存到萬代。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,14,"凡跌倒的、耶和華將他們扶持．凡被壓下的、將他們扶起。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,15,"萬民都舉目仰望你．你隨時給他們食物。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,16,"你張手、使有生氣的都隨願飽足。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,17,"耶和華在他一切所行的、無不公義．在他一切所作的、都有慈愛。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,18,"凡求告耶和華的、就是誠心求告他的、耶和華便與他們相近。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,19,"敬畏他的、他必成就他們的心願．也必聽他們的呼求、拯救他們。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,20,"耶和華保護一切愛他的人、卻要滅絕一切的惡人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",145,21,"我的口要說出讚美耶和華的話．惟願凡有血氣的、都永永遠遠稱頌他的聖名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,1,"你們要讚美耶和華。我的心哪、你要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,2,"我一生要讚美耶和華．我還活的時候、要歌頌我的　神。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,3,"你們不要倚靠君王、不要倚靠世人、他一點不能幫助。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,4,"他的氣一斷、就歸回塵土．他所打算的、當日就消滅了。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,5,"以雅各的　神為幫助、仰望耶和華他　神的、這人便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,6,"耶和華造天、地、海、、和其中的萬物．他守誠實、直到永遠．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,7,"他為受屈的伸冤、賜食物與飢餓的。耶和華釋放被囚的．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,8,"耶和華開了瞎子的眼睛．耶和華扶起被壓下的人．耶和華喜愛義人．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,9,"耶和華保護寄居的、扶持孤兒和寡婦．卻使惡人的道路彎曲。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",146,10,"耶和華要作王、直到永遠。錫安哪、你的　神要作王、直到萬代。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,1,"你們要讚美耶和華、因歌頌我們的　神為善為美．讚美的話是合宜的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,2,"耶和華建造耶路撒冷、聚集以色列中被趕散的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,3,"他醫好傷心的人、裹好他們的傷處。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,4,"他數點星宿的數目、一一稱他的名。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,5,"我們的主為大、最有能力．他的智慧、無法測度。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,6,"耶和華扶持謙卑人、將惡人傾覆於地。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,7,"你們要以感謝向耶和華歌唱、用琴向我們的　神歌頌。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,8,"他用雲遮天。為地降雨、使草生長在山上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,9,"他賜食給走獸、和啼叫的小烏鴉。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,10,"他不喜悅馬的力大、不喜愛人的腿快。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,11,"耶和華喜愛敬畏他、和盼望他慈愛的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,12,"耶路撒冷阿、你要頌讚耶和華．錫安哪、你要讚美你的　神。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,13,"因為他堅固了你的門閂、賜福給你中間的兒女。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,14,"他使你境內平安．用上好的麥子使你滿足。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,15,"他發命在地．他的話頒行最快。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,16,"他降雪如羊毛、撒霜如爐灰。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,17,"他擲下冰雹如碎渣．他發出寒冷、誰能當得起呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,18,"他一出令、這些就都消化．他使風颳起、水便流動。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,19,"他將他的道指示雅各、將他的律例典章指示以色列。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",147,20,"別國他都沒有這樣待過．至於他的典章、他們向來沒有知道。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,1,"你們要讚美耶和華、從天上讚美耶和華、在高處讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,2,"他的眾使者都要讚美他．他的諸軍都要讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,3,"日頭月亮、你們要讚美他．放光的星宿、你們都要讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,4,"天上的天、和天上的水、你們都要讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,5,"願這些都讚美耶和華的名．因他一吩咐便都造成。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,6,"他將這些立定、直到永永遠遠．他定了命、不能廢去。〔廢去或作越過〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,7,"所有在地上的、大魚和一切深洋、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,8,"火與冰雹、雪和霧氣、成就他命的狂風、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,9,"大山和小山、結果的樹木、和一切香柏樹、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,10,"野獸和一切牲畜、昆蟲和飛鳥、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,11,"世上的君王和萬民、首領和世上一切審判官、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,12,"少年人和處女、老年人和孩童、都當讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,13,"願這些都讚美耶和華的名．因為獨有他的名被尊崇．他的榮耀在天地之上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",148,14,"他將他百姓的角高舉．因此他〔因此他或作他使〕一切聖民以色列人、就是與他相近的百姓、都讚美他。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,1,"你們要讚美耶和華、向耶和華唱新歌、在聖民的會中讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,2,"願以色列因造他的主歡喜．願錫安的民、因他們的王快樂。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,3,"願他們跳舞讚美他的名、擊鼓彈琴歌頌他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,4,"因為耶和華喜愛他的百姓．他要用救恩當作謙卑人的妝飾。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,5,"願聖民因所得的榮耀高興．願他們在床上歡呼。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,6,"願他們口中稱讚　神為高、手裡有兩刃的刀．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,7,"為要報復列邦、刑罰萬民．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,8,"要用鍊子捆他們的君王、用鐵鐐鎖他們的大臣．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",149,9,"要在他們身上施行所記錄的審判．他的聖民都有這榮耀。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,1,"你們要讚美耶和華、在　神的聖所讚美他、在他顯能力的穹蒼讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,2,"要因他大能的作為讚美他、按著他極美的大德讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,3,"要用角聲讚美他、鼓瑟彈琴讚美他．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,4,"擊鼓跳舞讚美他、用絲絃的樂器、和簫的聲音讚美他．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,5,"用大響的鈸讚美他、用高聲的鈸讚美他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Psm",150,6,"凡有氣息的、都要讚美耶和華。你們要讚美耶和華。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,1,"以色列王大衛兒子所羅門的箴言．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,2,"要使人曉得智慧和訓誨．分辨通達的言語．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,3,"使人處事．領受智慧、仁義、公平、正直的訓誨．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,4,"使愚人靈明、使少年人有知識和謀略．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,5,"使智慧人聽見、增長學問、使聰明人得著智謀、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,6,"使人明白箴言和譬喻、懂得智慧人的言詞和謎語。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,7,"敬畏耶和華是知識的開端．愚妄人藐視智慧和訓誨。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,8,"我兒、要聽你父親的訓誨、不可離棄你母親的法則〔或作指教〕．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,9,"因為這要作你頭上的華冠、你項上的金鍊。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,10,"我兒、惡人若引誘你、你不可隨從。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,11,"他們若說、你與我們同去、我們要埋伏流人之血、要蹲伏害無罪之人．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,12,"我們好像陰間、把他們活活吞下．他們如同下坑的人、被我們囫圇吞了．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,13,"我們必得各樣寶物、將所擄來的裝滿房屋．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,14,"你與我們大家同分．我們共用一個囊袋。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,15,"我兒、不要與他們同行一道．禁止你腳走他們的路．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,16,"因為他們的腳奔跑行惡、他們急速流人的血。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,17,"好像飛鳥、網羅設在眼前仍不躲避．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,18,"這些人埋伏、是為自流己血．蹲伏、是為自害己命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,19,"凡貪戀財利的、所行之路、都是如此．這貪戀之心、乃奪去得財者之命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,20,"智慧在街市上呼喊、在寬闊處發聲．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,21,"在熱鬧街頭喊叫、在城門口、在城中發出言語．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,22,"說、你們愚昧人喜愛愚昧、褻慢人喜歡褻慢、愚頑人恨惡知識、要到幾時呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,23,"你們當因我的責備回轉．我要將我的靈澆灌你們、將我的話指示你們。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,24,"我呼喚、你們不肯聽從．我伸手、無人理會．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,25,"反輕棄我一切的勸戒、不肯受我的責備。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,26,"你們遭災難、我就發笑．驚恐臨到你們、我必嗤笑．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,27,"驚恐臨到你們、好像狂風、災難來到、如同暴風．急難痛苦臨到你們身上．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,28,"那時、你們必呼求我、我卻不答應、懇切的尋找我、卻尋不見．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,29,"因為你們恨惡知識、不喜愛敬畏耶和華、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,30,"不聽我的勸戒、藐視我一切的責備、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,31,"所以必喫自結的果子、充滿自設的計謀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,32,"愚昧人背道、必殺己身．愚頑人安逸、必害己命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",1,33,"惟有聽從我的、必安然居住、得享安靜、不怕災禍。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,1,"我兒、你若領受我的言語、存記我的命令、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,2,"側耳聽智慧、專心求聰明．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,3,"呼求明哲、揚聲求聰明、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,4,"尋找他如尋找銀子、搜求他如搜求隱藏的珍寶、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,5,"你就明白敬畏耶和華、得以認識　神。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,6,"因為、耶和華賜人智慧．知識和聰明都由他口而出．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,7,"他給正直人存留真智慧、給行為純正的人作盾牌．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,8,"為要保守公平人的路、護庇虔敬人的道．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,9,"你也必明白仁義、公平、正直、一切的善道。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,10,"智慧必入你心．你的靈要以知識為美．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,11,"謀略必護衛你．聰明必保守你．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,12,"要救你脫離惡道〔惡道或作惡人的道〕、脫離說乖謬話的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,13,"那等人捨棄正直的路、行走黑暗的道、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,14,"歡喜作惡、喜愛惡人的乖僻．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,15,"在他們的道中彎曲、在他們的路上偏僻。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,16,"智慧要救你脫離淫婦、就是那油嘴滑舌的外女．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,17,"他離棄幼年的配偶、忘了　神的盟約．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,18,"他的家陷入死地、他的路偏向陰間．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,19,"凡到他那裡去的不得轉回、也得不著生命的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,20,"智慧必使你行善人的道、守義人的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,21,"正直人必在世上居住．完全人必在地上存留。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",2,22,"惟有惡人必然剪除．奸詐的、必然拔出。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,1,"我兒、不要忘記我的法則．〔或作指教〕你心要謹守我的誡命．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,2,"因為他必將長久的日子、生命的年數、與平安、加給你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,3,"不可使慈愛誠實離開你．要繫在你頸項上、刻在你心版上．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,4,"這樣、你必在　神和世人眼前蒙恩寵、有聰明。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,5,"你要專心仰賴耶和華、不可倚靠自己的聰明．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,6,"在你一切所行的事上、都要認定他、他必指引你的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,7,"不要自以為有智慧．要敬畏耶和華、遠離惡事．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,8,"這便醫治你的肚臍、滋潤你的百骨。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,9,"你要以財物和一切初熟的土產、尊榮耶和華．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,10,"這樣、你的倉房、必充滿有餘、你的酒醡、有新酒盈溢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,11,"我兒、你不可輕看耶和華的管教〔或作懲治〕、也不可厭煩他的責備．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,12,"因為耶和華所愛的、他必責備．正如父親責備所喜愛的兒子。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,13,"得智慧、得聰明的、這人便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,14,"因為得智慧勝過得銀子、其利益強如精金．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,15,"比珍珠〔或作紅寶石〕寶貴．你一切所喜愛的、都不足與比較。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,16,"他右手有長壽．左手有富貴。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,17,"他的道是安樂、他的路全是平安。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,18,"他與持守他的作生命樹．持定他的俱各有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,19,"耶和華以智慧立地．以聰明定天．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,20,"以知識使深淵裂開、使天空滴下甘露。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,21,"我兒、要謹守真智慧和謀略．不可使他離開你的眼目．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,22,"這樣、他必作你的生命、頸項的美飾。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,23,"你就坦然行路、不至碰腳。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,24,"你躺下、必不懼怕．你躺臥、睡得香甜。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,25,"忽然來的驚恐、不要害怕．惡人遭毀滅、也不要恐懼．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,26,"因為耶和華是你所倚靠的．他必保守你的腳不陷入網羅。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,27,"你手若有行善的力量、不可推辭、就當向那應得的人施行。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,28,"你那裡若有現成的、不可對鄰舍說、去罷、明天再來、我必給你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,29,"你的鄰舍、既在你附近安居、你不可設計害他。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,30,"人未曾加害與你、不可無故與他相爭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,31,"不可嫉妒強暴的人、也不可選擇他所行的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,32,"因為乖僻人為耶和華所憎惡．正直人為他所親密。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,33,"耶和華咒詛惡人的家庭、賜福與義人的居所。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,34,"他譏誚那好譏誚的人、賜恩給謙卑的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",3,35,"智慧人必承受尊榮．愚昧人高陞也成為羞辱。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,1,"眾子阿、要聽父親的教訓、留心得知聰明．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,2,"因我所給你們的、是好教訓．不可離棄我的法則〔或作指教〕。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,3,"我在父親面前為孝子、在母親眼中為獨一的嬌兒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,4,"父親教訓我說、你心要存記我的言語、遵守我的命令、便得存活。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,5,"要得智慧、要得聰明、不可忘記、也不可偏離我口中的言語．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,6,"不可離棄智慧、智慧就護衛你．要愛他、他就保守你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,7,"智慧為首．所以要得智慧．在你一切所得之內、必得聰明。〔或作用你一切所得的去換聰明〕。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,8,"高舉智慧、他就使你高陞．懷抱智慧、他就使你尊榮。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,9,"他必將華冠加在你頭上、把榮冕交給你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,10,"我兒、你要聽受我的言語、就必延年益壽。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,11,"我已指教你走智慧的道、引導你行正直的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,12,"你行走、腳步必不致狹窄．你奔跑、也不致跌倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,13,"要持定訓誨、不可放鬆．必當謹守、因為他是你的生命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,14,"不可行惡人的路．不要走壞人的道。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,15,"要躲避、不可經過．要轉身而去。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,16,"這等人若不行惡、不得睡覺．不使人跌倒、睡臥不安。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,17,"因為他們以奸惡喫餅、以強暴喝酒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,18,"但義人的路、好像黎明的光、越照越明、直到日午。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,19,"惡人的道、好像幽暗．自己不知因甚麼跌倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,20,"我兒、要留心聽我的言詞、側耳聽我的話語．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,21,"都不可離你的眼目．要存記在你心中。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,22,"因為得著他的、就得了生命、又得了醫全體的良藥。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,23,"你要保守你心、勝過保守一切〔或作你要切切保守你心〕因為一生的果效、是由心發出。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,24,"你要除掉邪僻的口、棄絕乖謬的嘴。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,25,"你的眼目、要向前正看你的眼睛〔原文作皮〕當向前直觀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,26,"要修平你腳下的路、堅定你一切的道。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",4,27,"不可偏向左右．要使你的腳離開邪惡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,1,"我兒、要留心我智慧的話語、側耳聽我聰明的言詞．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,2,"為要使你謹守謀略、嘴唇保存知識。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,3,"因為淫婦的嘴滴下蜂蜜、他的口比油更滑．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,4,"至終卻苦似茵蔯、快如兩刃的刀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,5,"他的腳、下入死地．他腳步、踏住陰間．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,6,"以致他找不著生命平坦的道．他的路變遷不定、自己還不知道。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,7,"眾子阿、現在要聽從我、不可離棄我口中的話。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,8,"你所行的道要離他遠、不可就近他的房門．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,9,"恐怕將你的尊榮給別人、將你的歲月給殘忍的人．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,10,"恐怕外人滿得你的力量、你勞碌得來的、歸入外人的家．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,11,"終久你皮肉和身體消毀、你就悲歎、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,12,"說、我怎麼恨惡訓誨、心中藐視責備、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,13,"也不聽從我師傅的話、又不側耳聽那教訓我的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,14,"我在聖會裡、幾乎落在諸般惡中。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,15,"你要喝自己池中的水、飲自己井裡的活水。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,16,"你的泉源豈可漲溢在外．你的河水豈可流在街上．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,17,"惟獨歸你一人、不可與外人同用。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,18,"要使你的泉源蒙福．要喜悅你幼年所娶的妻。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,19,"他如可愛的麀鹿、可喜的母鹿．願他的胸懷、使你時時知足．他的愛情、使你常常戀慕。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,20,"我兒、你為何戀慕淫婦、為何抱外女的胸懷．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,21,"因為人所行的道、都在耶和華眼前．他也修平人一切的路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,22,"惡人必被自己的罪孽捉住．他必被自己的罪惡如繩索纏繞。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",5,23,"他因不受訓誨、就必死亡．又因愚昧過甚、必走差了路。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,1,"我兒、你若為朋友作保、替外人擊掌、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,2,"你就被口中的話語纏住、被嘴裡的言語捉住。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,3,"我兒、你既落在朋友手中、就當這樣行、纔可救自己．你要自卑、去懇求你的朋友．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,4,"不要容你的眼睛睡覺、不要容你的眼皮打盹．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,5,"要救自己、如鹿脫離獵戶的手、如鳥脫離捕鳥人的手。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,6,"懶惰人哪、你去察看螞蟻的動作、就可得智慧．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,7,"螞蟻沒有元帥、沒有官長、沒有君王、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,8,"尚且在夏天預備食物、在收割時聚斂糧食。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,9,"懶惰人哪、你要睡到幾時呢．你何時睡醒呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,10,"再睡片時、打盹片時、抱著手躺臥片時、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,11,"你的貧窮就必如強盜速來、你的缺乏彷彿拿兵器的人來到。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,12,"無賴的惡徒、行動就用乖僻的口．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,13,"用眼傳神、用腳示意、用指點劃．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,14,"心中乖僻、常設惡謀、布散分爭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,15,"所以災難必忽然臨到他身．他必頃刻敗壞無法可治。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,16,"耶和華所恨惡的有六樣、連他心所憎惡的共有七樣．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,17,"就是高傲的眼、撒謊的舌、流無辜人血的手、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,18,"圖謀惡計的心、飛跑行惡的腳、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,19,"吐謊言的假見證、並弟兄中布散分爭的人。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,20,"我兒、要謹守你父親的誡命、不可離棄你母親的法則．〔或作指教〕")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,21,"要常繫在你心上、掛在你項上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,22,"你行走、他必引導你．你躺臥、他必保守你．你睡醒、他必與你談論。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,23,"因為誡命是燈．法則〔或作指教〕是光、訓誨的責備是生命的道．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,24,"能保你遠離惡婦、遠離外女諂媚的舌頭。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,25,"你心中不要戀慕他的美色、也不要被他眼皮勾引。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,26,"因為妓女能使人只剩一塊餅、淫婦獵取人寶貴的生命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,27,"人若懷裡搋火、衣服豈能不燒呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,28,"人若在火炭上走、腳豈能不燙呢。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,29,"親近鄰舍之妻的、也是如此．凡挨近他的、不免受罰。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,30,"賊因飢餓偷竊充飢、人不藐視他．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,31,"若被找著、他必賠還七倍．必將家中所有的、盡都償還。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,32,"與婦人行淫的、便是無知、行這事的、必喪掉生命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,33,"他必受傷損、必被凌辱．他的羞恥不得塗抹。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,34,"因為人的嫉恨、成了烈怒．報仇的時候、決不留情。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",6,35,"甚麼贖價、他都不顧．你雖送許多禮物、他也不肯干休。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,1,"我兒、你要遵守我的言語、將我的命令存記在心．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,2,"遵守我的命令、就得存活．保守我的法則〔或作指教〕好像保守眼中的瞳人．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,3,"繫在你指頭上、刻在你心版上。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,4,"對智慧說、你是我的姊妹．稱呼聰明為你的親人．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,5,"他就保你遠離淫婦、遠離說諂媚話的外女。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,6,"我曾在我房屋的窗戶內、從我窗櫺之間、往外觀看．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,7,"見愚蒙人內、少年人中、分明有一個無知的少年人、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,8,"從街上經過、走近淫婦的巷口、直往通他家的路去、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,9,"在黃昏、或晚上、或半夜、或黑暗之中、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,10,"看哪、有一個婦人來迎接他、是妓女的打扮、有詭詐的心思。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,11,"這婦人喧嚷不守約束、在家裡停不住腳．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,12,"有時在街市上、有時在寬闊處、或在各巷口蹲伏．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,13,"拉住那少年人、與他親嘴、臉無羞恥對他說、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,14,"平安祭在我這裡．今日纔還了我所許的願。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,15,"因此、我出來迎接你、懇切求見你的面、恰巧遇見了你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,16,"我已經用繡花毯子、和埃及線織的花紋布、鋪了我的床。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,17,"我又用沒藥、沉香、桂皮薰了我的榻。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,18,"你來、我們可以飽享愛情、直到早晨．我們可以彼此親愛歡樂。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,19,"因為我丈夫不在家、出門行遠路．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,20,"他手拿銀囊．必到月望纔回家。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,21,"淫婦用許多巧言誘他隨從、用諂媚的嘴逼他同行。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,22,"少年人立刻跟隨他、好像牛往宰殺之地、又像愚昧人帶鎖鍊、去受刑罰．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,23,"直等箭穿他的肝、如同雀鳥急入網羅、卻不知是自喪己命。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,24,"眾子阿、現在要聽從我、留心聽我口中的話。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,25,"你的心、不可偏向淫婦的道．不要入他的迷途。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,26,"因為被他傷害僕倒的不少．被他殺戮的而且甚多。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",7,27,"他的家是在陰間之路、下到死亡之宮。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,1,"智慧豈不呼叫、聰明豈不發聲。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,2,"他在道旁高處的頂上、在十字路口站立．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,3,"在城門旁、在城門口、在城門洞、大聲說、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,4,"眾人哪、我呼叫你們．我向世人發聲。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,5,"說、愚蒙人哪、你們要會悟靈明．愚昧人哪、你們當心裡明白。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,6,"你們當聽、因我要說極美的話．我張嘴要論正直的事。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,7,"我的口要發出真理．我的嘴憎惡邪惡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,8,"我口中的言語、都是公義、並無彎曲乖僻。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,9,"有聰明的以為明顯、得知識的以為正直．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,10,"你們當受我的教訓、不受白銀．寧得知識、勝過黃金。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,11,"因為智慧比珍珠〔或作紅寶石〕更美．一切可喜愛的、都不足與比較。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,12,"我智慧以靈明為居所、又尋得知識和謀略。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,13,"敬畏耶和華、在乎恨惡邪惡．那驕傲、狂妄、並惡道、以及乖謬的口、都為我所恨惡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,14,"我有謀略、和真知識．我乃聰明．我有能力。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,15,"帝王藉我坐國位．君王藉我定公平。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,16,"王子和首領、世上一切的審判官、都是藉我掌權。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,17,"愛我的、我也愛他．懇切尋求我的、必尋得見。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,18,"豐富尊榮在我．恆久的財並公義也在我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,19,"我的果實勝過黃金．強如精金．我的出產超乎高銀。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,20,"我在公義的道上走、在公平的路中行．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,21,"使愛我的承受貨財、並充滿他們的府庫。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,22,"在耶和華造化的起頭、在太初創造萬物之先、就有了我。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,23,"從亙古、從太初、未有世界以前、我已被立。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,24,"沒有深淵、沒有大水的泉源、我已生出。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,25,"大山未曾奠定、小山未有之先、我已生出。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,26,"耶和華還沒有創造大地、和田野、並世上的土質、我已生出。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,27,"他立高天、我在那裡．他在淵面的周圍、劃出圓圈、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,28,"上使穹蒼堅硬、下使淵源穩固、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,29,"為滄海定出界限、使水不越過他的命令、立定大地的根基．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,30,"那時、我在他那裡為工師、日日為他所喜愛、常常在他面前踴躍、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,31,"踴躍在他為人預備可住之地、也喜悅住在世人之間。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,32,"眾子阿、現在要聽從我．因為謹守我道的、便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,33,"要聽教訓、就得智慧、不可棄絕。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,34,"聽從我、日日在我門口仰望、在我門框旁邊等候的、那人便為有福。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,35,"因為尋得我的、就尋得生命、也必蒙耶和華的恩惠。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",8,36,"得罪我的、卻害了自己的性命．恨惡我的、都喜愛死亡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,1,"智慧建造房屋、鑿成七根柱子、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,2,"宰殺牲畜、調和旨酒、設擺筵席．")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,3,"打發使女出去、自己在城中至高處呼叫、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,4,"說、誰是愚蒙人、可以轉到這裡來．又對那無知的人說、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,5,"你們來、喫我的餅、喝我調和的酒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,6,"你們愚蒙人、要捨棄愚蒙、就得存活．並要走光明的道。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,7,"指斥褻慢人的、必受辱罵．責備惡人的、必被玷污。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,8,"不要責備褻慢人、恐怕他恨你．要責備智慧人、他必愛你。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,9,"教導智慧人、他就越發有智慧．指示義人、他就增長學問。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,10,"敬畏耶和華、是智慧的開端．認識至聖者、便是聰明。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,11,"你藉著我、日子必增多、年歲也必加添。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,12,"你若有智慧、是與自己有益．你若褻慢、就必獨自擔當。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,13,"愚昧的婦人喧嚷．他是愚蒙、一無所知。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,14,"他坐在自己的家門口、坐在城中高處的座位上、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,15,"呼叫過路的、就是直行其道的人、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,16,"說、誰是愚蒙人、可以轉到這裡來．又對那無知的人說、")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,17,"偷來的水是甜的、暗喫的餅是好的。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",9,18,"人卻不知有陰魂在他那裡．他的客在陰間的深處。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,1,"所羅門的箴言。智慧之子、使父親歡樂．愚昧之子、叫母親擔憂。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,2,"不義之財、毫無益處．惟有公義、能救人脫離死亡。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,3,"耶和華不使義人受飢餓．惡人所欲的他必推開。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,4,"手懶的、要受貧窮．手勤的、卻要富足。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,5,"夏天聚斂的、是智慧之子．收割時沉睡的、是貽羞之子。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,6,"福祉臨到義人的頭．強暴蒙蔽惡人的口。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,7,"義人的紀念被稱讚．惡人的名字必朽爛。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,8,"心中智慧的、必受命令．口裡愚妄的、必致傾倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,9,"行正直路的、步步安穩．走彎曲道的、必致敗露。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,10,"以眼傳神的、使人憂患．口裡愚妄的、必致傾倒。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,11,"義人的口是生命的泉源．強暴蒙蔽惡人的口。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,12,"恨、能挑啟爭端．愛、能遮掩一切過錯。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,13,"明哲人嘴裡有智慧．無知人背上受刑杖。")');
tx.executeSql('INSERT INTO bible ( writer , ch , node, text) VALUES ( "Pro",10,14,"智慧人積存知識．愚妄人的口速致敗壞。")');
